<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Posting Schedule — ImpactGrid Creator Engine</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css"/>
  <style>
    .sched-card { background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:var(--radius); padding:18px; }
    .sched-day { font-family:'Syne',sans-serif; font-weight:700; font-size:0.82rem; color:var(--orange); text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:1px; margin-bottom:10px; }
    .sched-slot { display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; padding:7px 0; border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); font-size:0.78rem; }
    .sched-slot:last-child { border-bottom:none; }
    .sched-time { color:var(--white-dim); }
    .platform-dot { display:inline-block; width:7px; height:7px; border-radius:50%; margin-right:5px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<aside class="sidebar" id="sidebar"></aside>
<div class="main">
  <div class="topbar">
    <div class="topbar-left">
      <button class="hamburger" onclick="openNav()">☰</button>
      <span class="topbar-page-title">Posting Schedule</span>
    </div>
    <div class="topbar-right">
      <a href="upload.html" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm">+ Upload Video</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="eyebrow">AI-Optimised Timing</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">Post at the <em>perfect time,</em><br>every time</h1>
    <p class="hero-desc">Our AI analyses your audience, your niche, and real-time platform data to tell you exactly when to post each piece of content for maximum reach.</p>
  </div>

  <section class="section fade-up">
    <p class="section-label">This Week's Schedule</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Your <em>7-day plan</em></h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Every slot is chosen based on when your specific audience is most active on each platform.</p>

    <div class="grid-auto-sm" style="margin-top:4px">
      <div class="sched-card">
        <div class="sched-day">Monday</div>
        <div class="sched-slot"><span class="sched-time">7:30 AM</span><span><span class="platform-dot" style="background:#e1306c"></span>IG Story</span></div>
        <div class="sched-slot"><span class="sched-time">12:00 PM</span><span><span class="platform-dot" style="background:#000"></span>TikTok Reel</span></div>
        <div class="sched-slot"><span class="sched-time">6:00 PM</span><span><span class="platform-dot" style="background:#0077b5"></span>LinkedIn Post</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="sched-card">
        <div class="sched-day">Tuesday</div>
        <div class="sched-slot"><span class="sched-time">8:00 AM</span><span><span class="platform-dot" style="background:#1da1f2"></span>X Thread</span></div>
        <div class="sched-slot"><span class="sched-time">5:30 PM</span><span><span class="platform-dot" style="background:#e1306c"></span>IG Reel</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="sched-card">
        <div class="sched-day">Wednesday</div>
        <div class="sched-slot"><span class="sched-time">7:00 AM</span><span><span class="platform-dot" style="background:#e1306c"></span>IG Story</span></div>
        <div class="sched-slot"><span class="sched-time">12:30 PM</span><span><span class="platform-dot" style="background:#e1306c"></span>Carousel</span></div>
        <div class="sched-slot"><span class="sched-time">7:00 PM</span><span><span class="platform-dot" style="background:#ff0000"></span>YT Short</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="sched-card">
        <div class="sched-day">Thursday</div>
        <div class="sched-slot"><span class="sched-time">9:00 AM</span><span><span class="platform-dot" style="background:#000"></span>TikTok</span></div>
        <div class="sched-slot"><span class="sched-time">6:00 PM</span><span><span class="platform-dot" style="background:#e1306c"></span>IG Reel</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="sched-card">
        <div class="sched-day">Friday</div>
        <div class="sched-slot"><span class="sched-time">7:30 AM</span><span><span class="platform-dot" style="background:#e1306c"></span>IG Story</span></div>
        <div class="sched-slot"><span class="sched-time">1:00 PM</span><span><span class="platform-dot" style="background:#e1306c"></span>Carousel</span></div>
        <div class="sched-slot"><span class="sched-time">5:00 PM</span><span><span class="platform-dot" style="background:#000"></span>TikTok</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="sched-card">
        <div class="sched-day">Saturday</div>
        <div class="sched-slot"><span class="sched-time">10:00 AM</span><span><span class="platform-dot" style="background:#e1306c"></span>Lifestyle Reel</span></div>
        <div class="sched-slot"><span class="sched-time">3:00 PM</span><span><span class="platform-dot" style="background:#000"></span>BTS TikTok</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="sched-card">
        <div class="sched-day">Sunday</div>
        <div class="sched-slot"><span class="sched-time">Rest day 😴</span><span style="color:var(--white-dim)">or schedule ahead</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section fade-up">
    <p class="section-label">Why Timing Matters</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">The <em>right time</em> doubles your reach</h2>
    <div class="grid-3">
      <div class="card" style="padding:22px">
        <div style="font-size:1.8rem;margin-bottom:10px">📈</div>
        <strong style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;display:block;margin-bottom:6px">Algorithm advantage</strong>
        <p style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--white-dim);line-height:1.5">Platforms push content that gets early engagement. Posting when your audience is online drives instant interaction.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:22px">
        <div style="font-size:1.8rem;margin-bottom:10px">🌍</div>
        <strong style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;display:block;margin-bottom:6px">Audience-specific</strong>
        <p style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--white-dim);line-height:1.5">Your business audience may peak at different times. We tailor schedules per niche, not generic averages.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card" style="padding:22px">
        <div style="font-size:1.8rem;margin-bottom:10px">🔄</div>
        <strong style="font-family:'Syne',sans-serif;display:block;margin-bottom:6px">Constantly updated</strong>
        <p style="font-size:0.78rem;color:var(--white-dim);line-height:1.5">Platform behaviour changes. Our schedule updates weekly based on the latest algorithm data.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="footer-brand"><div class="brand">ImpactGrid <em>Creator Engine</em></div><p>AI AI Content Platform</p></div>
    <div class="footer-links">
      <a href="index.html">Dashboard</a><a href="calendar.html">Calendar</a>
      <a href="trending.html">Trending</a><a href="contact.html">Contact</a>
      <a href="https://impactgridanalytics.com/" target="_blank" class="link-blue">Analytics ↗</a>
    </div>
    <p class="footer-copy">© 2025 ImpactGrid Creator Engine. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</div>
<script src="nav.js"></script>
<script>initNav('schedule.html');</script>
</body>
</html>
